Attention Adventists! This is the final boarding call for flight #GYD17. You've got 1 week to gather some friends to be the sermon on March 18. This is the largest social media and TMI (Total Member Involvement) activity in our history. Download the app here: www.globalyouthday.org

Help us caption & translate this video!

http://amara.org/v/4u6G/
